{"tid":2230985,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS5 改確認鍵為X取消鍵為O","createTime":"2020-10-05T10:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T14:36:40.000Z","uid":109356,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a700f6b7d826d2b6c43fe7cd3b049c182ec1e574","tid":2230985,"uid":109356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T10:29:38.000Z","msg":"日本記者西田宗千佳在他的 PlayStation 5 試玩報告中確認：SIE此後將統一PS5的按鍵操作，&times;為確認鍵、○為取消鍵<br />\n<br />\n以往，日系主機通常都使用右側的最右鍵為確認，任天堂的「A」鍵、日本PS的「○」鍵。而歐美地區則通常使用右側四鍵的最下鍵位確認，XBOX的「A」鍵、歐美PS的「&times;」鍵。這種差異在各種遊戲中都給玩家帶來了不小的麻煩，習慣了一側之後，玩另一種習慣的遊戲會經常按錯鍵。<br />\n<br />\nSIE這次決定包括日本遊戲在內的所有設定都將統一，官方說法是：「為了避免在多個國家的遊戲環境中，系統和遊戲之間使用的按鍵差異。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pcucgame.com/sony-playstation-5-will-unified-confirm-button-and-cancel-button/?fbclid=IwAR3UF6SsZf4VHeZsb4sR---Q6qtXsp3imulFFFrqN8bVhaHH3LVDx1zuDWQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpcucgame.com%2Fsony-playstation-5-will-unified-confirm-button-and-cancel-button%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3UF6SsZf4VHeZsb4sR---Q6qtXsp3imulFFFrqN8bVhaHH3LVDx1zuDWQ&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGFuZLtDw6XEhdFI90r4xbX0%3D&h=89e2ceed\" target=\"_blank\">https://pcucgame.com/sony-playstation-5-will-unified-confirm-button-and-cancel-button/?fbclid=IwAR3UF6SsZf4VHeZsb4sR---Q6qtXsp3imulFFFrqN8bVhaHH3LVDx1zuDWQ</a>"},{"pid":"5e9b8dc78ff23a1c626f8ae077f5304b77bd8eb4","tid":2230985,"uid":84013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T10:34:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母!"},{"pid":"6c0c36108af38975522dd5bbe14a8ab32f04b623","tid":2230985,"uid":109356,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T10:36:03.000Z","msg":"佢咁改完<br />\n我望到個交叉 係確認我覺得仲怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c01baf180786340b53fc2eba5a6894bea3cd59f","tid":2230985,"uid":247998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T10:37:05.000Z","msg":"最開頭都唔明點解歐美會轉 x 做 confirm ..."},{"pid":"66d19f21e8002a7da34db24447a4b4f119f9bd8b","tid":22309